    script.
      try{Typekit.load({ async: true });}catch(e){}
    
  body
    .wrapper
      header.hero.hero--foundation
        .row
          .top-bar
            .logo
              img(src='img/device.svg')
            nav.nav    
              ul
                a(href='index.html')
                  li Home
                li.course-btn courses
          
          
          .sub-nav
            .arrow
            ul
              li.active-sub Foundation Courses
              li
                a(href='business-and-finance.html') Business and Finance
              li 
                a(href='property-and-construction.html') Property and Construction
              li 
                a(href='sciences.html') Sciences


          .menu
            img(src='img/menu.svg')
    
        .row
          .hero__text
            .hero__title
              h1 Foundation  
                br 
                |  courses
          .hero__course-intro
            p If you don't have A-levels or equivalent qualifications, you can still access our world-class degrees by taking one of our foundation courses. These 1 year access courses will teach you the basics of the subject and develop your academic skills. 
            p If you successfully complete the foundation course, you'll be guaranteed progression to a degree course in the same subject area either in Malaysia or the UK, without needing to reapply.
          
          a.btn.red(href='#') How to apply
      
      section.course__container
        article.row
          .large-6.medium-6.columns
            h2.course__heading Foundation in Business
            p Get prepared for BA Management and Business, BSc Finance and Business Management, BSc Real Estate, BSc Quantity Surveying or BSc Psychology at the University of Reading Malaysia with this 1 year access course. 
            p Develop the academic skills that you'll need to succeed on a degree-level course and get an introduction into business and management that will prepare you for studying a range of courses in Malaysia or the UK. An English language module is available for students with an IELTS score below 6.5, or you could improve your English skills with one of our 
              a(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/learn/foundation-and-language-plus-programme') English language courses 
              | before you start.
            a.btn.red(href='#') How to apply
            a.btn.grey(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/learn/foundation-in-business') Find out more
          
          .large-6.medium-6.columns
            aside.fact-file
              img.fact-file__icon(src='img/fact-file.svg')
              h4 Fact file
              h5 Entry requirements
              ul
                li 
                  strong SPM: 
                  | Minimum of 5 at Grade C or above, excluding English for Science and Technology, Islamic Studies and Moral Studies
                li 
                  strong IGCSE: 
                  | 5 passes at Grade A – C in relevant subjects or an equivalent international qualification
                li 
                  strong SPM 1119: 
                  | Grade C
                li 
                  strong IELTS: 
                  | 5.5 (no element below 5.0).  Students entering in March or pursuing a law degree in the UK require IELTS 6.0 (no element below 5.0) 
      
      section.course__container
        article.row
          .large-6.medium-6.columns
            h2.course__heading Foundation in Science
            p Get prepared for BSc Psychology or Pharmacy at the University of Reading Malaysia with this 1 year access course.
            p Develop the academic skills that you'll need to succeed on a degree-level course and get an introduction into science and mathematics at a higher level that will prepare you for studying a range of courses in Malaysia or the UK. An English language module is available for students with an IELTS score below 6.5, or you could improve your English skills with one of our 
              a(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/learn/foundation-and-language-plus-programme') English language courses
              |  before you start.
            a.btn.red(href='#') How to apply
            a.btn.grey(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/learn/foundation-in-science') Find out more
          .large-6.medium-6.columns
            aside.fact-file
              img.fact-file__icon(src='img/fact-file.svg')
              h4 Fact file
              h5 Entry requirements
              strong For entry to M/BPharm degrees:
              ul
                li 
                  strong SPM: 
                  | Minimum of 5 Grade Bs in Mathematics or Additional Mathematics, Biology, Chemistry, Physics and one other subject.
              strong For entry to all other Science degrees:   
              ul  
                li 
                  strong SPM: 
                  | Minimum of 5 at Grade C or above, excluding English for Science and Technology, Islamic Studies and Moral Studies
                li 
                  strong IGCSE: 
                  | 5 passes at Grade A – C in relevant subjects or an equivalent international qualification
                li 
                  strong SPM 1119: 
                  | Grade C
                li 
                  strong IELTS: 
                  | 5.0 (no element below 4.5)
              
      section
        .row
          .large-12.columns
            aside.other-courses
              ul
                li
                  strong Other courses 
                li
                  a(href='business-and-finance.html') Business and Finance 
                li
                  a(href='property-and-construction.html') Property and Construction 
                li
                  a(href='sciences.html') Sciences

